'''Elise Nilsson''' (b. January 17, 1904 — d. ???) is the former Swedian baroness, born to [[Lars Nilsson]] and Molly Nilsson, the legal heir to a fifth of her father's estate and the secondary successor of the Nilsson branch. At birth she was identified as the Baroness of Lerum.<br>
